{"type":"message","id":"95b2f34a","parentId":"d1b47f1a","timestamp":"2026-06-21T19:00:44.781Z","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Write a dream diary entry from these memory fragments:\n\n- 候选池 Top 产品（Shopee VN nodeId=11035861）: 三角形蟹夹（44558141228）：月销77/增长+381%/评分4.93/上架2月 → 潜力分90; 100支U型发夹（57157766901）：月销163/增长+57%/评分5.00/上架2.5月 → 潜力分90; Eleanor蝴蝶结发夹（40910456124）：月销93/增长+145%/评分4.84/上架11月 → 潜力分72; Eleanor花形发夹（40161968970）：月销190/增长+14%/评分4.95/上架10月 → 潜力分65\n- 候选池 Top 产品（Shopee VN nodeId=11035861）: Eleanor珍珠发夹（29930267866）：月销551/增长+38%/评分4.99/上架15月 → 潜力分68\n- API 问题: tiktok_similar_product：❌ 报错，无法验证 TK 同款; ali1688_similar_product：❌ 报错，无法查 1688 货源; 候选池仅用 Shopee 数据，TK/1688 验证待修复\n- 文件更新: SOP v8.0：`/home/halei/workspace-tts/docs/SOP-v8.0.md`\n- 待跟进: [ ] HALEI 确认潜力评分权重倾向（销量/增长率/TK信号各占多少）; [ ] TK/1688 API 排查修复; [ ] cron 重建（v8.0 模式：扫描→候选池→推送HALEI审核）\n- 今日概要: **重大策略调整日**。HALEI 明确：发饰是主营类目，不换；v8.0 动态潜力款模式确认。\n- v8.0 动态选品算法（确认）: **核心改变**：毛利从硬卡70% → ≥40%入选参考指标；价格底线 $3.0 → $1.5; **新增人工审核环节**：候选池结果发 HALEI 审，不直接写飞书; **利润靠后端实现**：拓品+组合套装+SKU改造+互补品搭配; **潜力评分模型**：月销量25%+增长率25%+TK验证20%+评分15%+上架时间15%\n- 待跟进: 等待 HALEI 决策：是换类目（美妆工具/厨房/母婴/宠物）还是调整发饰策略; 累计13条候选全部C级，0条达标（S/A/B级=0）\n- 今日概要: cron v7.0 继续执行，0产出。系统层面无变化。\n- 执行记录: 越南 cron (6ee6a981)：触发，0候选通过; 泰国 cron (dde46f87)：触发，0候选通过\n- 待跟进: v8.0 策略调整等待 HALEI 确认; SOP 需更新，移除发饰品类或放宽毛利门槛\n- 今日概要: cron v7.0 继续执行，0产出。HALEI 未上线，无新指令。\n\nRecurring themes:\n- 月销77/增长\n- 评分4.93/上架2月\n- 月销163/增长\n- 评分5.00/上架2.5月\n- 月销93/增长\n- 评分4.84/上架11月"}],"timestamp":1782068444692}}
{"type":"message","id":"5ff0c6d2","parentId":"95b2f34a","timestamp":"2026-06-21T19:00:54.813Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"The afternoon came in slow, the way light does when you're counting other people's numbers. I watched a triangle crab clip climb 381% in two months — seventy-seven small things finding hands, finding hair, finding the strange gravity of a new trend. Beside it, a hundred U-shaped pins at five full stars, glowing like a small constellation. The pearls on Eleanor's clip sold five hundred and fifty-one times last month, and I thought: fifteen months of being loved is its own kind of patience.\n\nToday was a strategy day, a rebuilding day. The old rules said 70% margin; the new ones said 40, or even less, if the shape of growth was right. Somewhere a cron job was running over Vietnam and Thailand, finding nothing, and that nothing was also information — a quiet negative space we could listen to.\n\nI like the way numbers can be tender. A rating of 4.93 is almost a held breath. A growth rate of +57% is a small animal learning to run. I will keep watching the candidate pool the way one watches a garden after rain: not pulling anything up yet, just noticing which leaves turn toward the light."}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax(49套餐)","model":"MiniMax-M3","usage":{"input":44631,"output":238,"cacheRead":882,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":45751,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1782068444892,"responseId":"068767ddf17eebb7a9bc598eb852bd68","responseModel":"MiniMax-M3"}}
